                <h2>Peace Of Mind</h2>

                 <p>All staff are DBS checked, First Aid trained and fully insured. We take your pets care seriously and are licenced with Leeds City Council. Our friendly staff are available to answer any questions you have and will if requested provide you with regular updates and pictures.</p>

            </div>

        </div>

    </section>

          

